title: Wildfire prompts M.D. Anderson to evacuate Bastrop facility
text:
Published By: Houston Chronicle Texas - Today 
The M.D. Anderson Cancer Center's Science Park was evacuated Tuesday afternoon as crews battled one of several brush fires in Bastrop County...
